g.aria-label: Hold down the button and rotate the knob (brightness changes only affect your heart)

text.tspan: Blue: Connected to the internet, but Chelsey is offline
Red: Cannot connect to the internet. Will keep retrying in
background. Reboot to change wifi network (setup mode)
Orange/Yellow: Setup Mode (could not connect to
previously saved wifi). On your phone/laptop,
connect to the wifi called "Blaine Heart Setup",
and if not automatically redirected, go to
192.168.4.1 in a web browser. Or reboot to
retry connecting to previously saved wifi
